body.p: The following Northmen have bought or sold real estate:
1. Hawgart Ave., Cor. Hayes Ave., O.W.Peterson to Axel Peterson. Price $1,750.
2. Sawyer Ave., South of Belden Ave., S. Seversen to Fred Housfeld. Price $5,900.
3.Green St. South of 60th St., J.W. Johnson to Nels A. Nelson. Price $8,000.
4. Yale Ave., South of 78th St., H.H.Mattison to W.C.Shipnes. Price $3,000.
5. Cornelia St., West of Campbell Ave., K. Johnson to Johannes G. Thumes. Price $4,950.
6. Cornelia St. East of Washtenaw Ave., John Berg, to George O. Johnson. Price $10,000.
7. N. 51st Court., Cor. Indiana St., Charles Parson to Anna E. Johnson. Price $7,200.
8. Humboldt Blvd., cor. Humboldt St., C. Rolandsen to S.A. Hemmi. Price $21,500.
9. Potomac Ave., cor. Leavitt St., W. C. Anderson to Netty Farber. Price $14,500.
